name: Purpose Silver Bullion Fund
longDescription: Silver Bullion Trust is a self governing closedend trust with voting rights that provides the secure holding of silver bullion on behalf of its Unit holders. The ETF has been created to buy and hold substantially all of its assets in silver bullion and, incidental thereto, minoramounts of silver certificates, if any.
